Add `opentelemetry-instrumentation-agno`, instrumenting the `agno` agent
framework (`Agent.run` / `Agent.arun` agent invocations and
`FunctionCall.execute` tool executions), emitting standard GenAI semantic
conventions (`gen_ai.*`) via `opentelemetry-util-genai`. Requires
`OTEL_SEMCONV_STABILITY_OPT_IN=gen_ai_latest_experimental`.
